      <title>signal quick start</title>
      <link href="/sharewithyou/2021/11/02/signal-quick-start/"/>
      <url>/sharewithyou/2021/11/02/signal-quick-start/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;<code>Signal</code>是一个基于<code>SpringBoot</code>和<code>Netty</code>的通讯项目，它提供了基于XML配置文件创建<code>Server</code>、<code>Client</code>和<code>Task</code>的功能。这意味着，在大多数情况下，用户只需要编写XML配置文件即可。与此同时，<code>Signal</code>提供了良好的拓展性，很多功能点用户可以根据自己的需求去定制自己的实现，当然这需要用户了解<code>Netty</code>框架，在后面会详细介绍拓展功能。</p><h2 id="Quick-Start"><a href="#Quick-Start" class="headerlink" title="Quick Start"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id="serverConfig-xml"><a href="#serverConfig-xml" class="headerlink" title="serverConfig.xml"></a><span style="color:red">serverConfig.xml</span></h3><p>打开<code>resources</code>-&gt;<code>config</code>-&gt;<code>serverConfig.xml</code></p><p>除去注释部分，可以看到如下配置</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">config</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">container</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;oneToSignal&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">server</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;template_server&quot;</span> <span class="attr">port</span>=<span class="string">&quot;21101&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">inExcel</span> <span class="attr">excelName</span>=<span class="string">&quot;template&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">server</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">container</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">config</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>标签：config</p></blockquote><p><code>config</code>：根标签。类似于大部分XML文件的<code>root</code>标签。</p><blockquote><p>标签：container</p></blockquote><p><code>container</code>：容器标签。与<code>type</code>属性一起指定创建何种类型的<code>server</code>。</p><blockquote><p>标签：<span style="color:red">server</span></p></blockquote><p><span style="color:red"><code>server</code></span>：用户需要重点关注的标签，用户可以参考样例修改自己的配置，以创建或修改<code>server</code>。一般来说，<code>name</code>属性和<code>port</code>属性所有的<code>server</code>都会具有，而其他属性或子标签都与具体的实现相关。</p><h3 id="clientConfig-xml"><a href="#clientConfig-xml" class="headerlink" title="clientConfig.xml"></a><span style="color:red">clientConfig.xml</span></h3><p>打开<code>resources</code>-&gt;<code>config</code>-&gt;<code>clientConfig.xml</code></p><p>除去注释部分，可以看到如下配置（与serverConfig.xml类似）</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">config</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">container</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;signalToOne&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">client</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;template_client&quot;</span> <span class="attr">host</span>=<span class="string">&quot;127.0.0.1&quot;</span> <span class="attr">port</span>=<span class="string">&quot;21101&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">outExcel</span> <span class="attr">excelName</span>=<span class="string">&quot;template&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">client</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">container</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">container</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;signalToProcess&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">client</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;process_control&quot;</span> <span class="attr">host</span>=<span class="string">&quot;192.168.100.100&quot;</span> <span class="attr">port</span>=<span class="string">&quot;22110&quot;</span> </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">                <span class="attr">exchangeName</span>=<span class="string">&quot;process_exchange&quot;</span> <span class="attr">routingKey</span>=<span class="string">&quot;process_accept_queue&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">container</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">container</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;signalToProcessAlarm&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">client</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;process_alarm&quot;</span> <span class="attr">host</span>=<span class="string">&quot;192.168.100.100&quot;</span> <span class="attr">port</span>=<span class="string">&quot;6000&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">container</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">config</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>标签：config</p></blockquote><p><code>config</code>：根标签。类似于大部分XML文件的<code>root</code>标签。</p><blockquote><p>标签：container</p></blockquote><p><code>container</code>：容器标签。与<code>type</code>属性一起指定创建何种类型的<code>client</code>。</p><blockquote><p>标签：<span style="color:red">client</span></p></blockquote><p><span style="color:red"><code>client</code></span>：用户需要重点关注的标签，用户可以参考样例修改自己的配置，以创建或修改<code>client</code>。一般来说，<code>name</code>属性、<code>host</code>属性和<code>port</code>属性所有的<code>client</code>都会具有，而其他属性或子标签都与具体的实现相关。</p><h3 id="mqConfig-xml"><a href="#mqConfig-xml" class="headerlink" title="mqConfig.xml"></a>mqConfig.xml</h3><p><code>resources</code>-&gt;<code>config</code>-&gt;<code>mqConfig.xml</code>（可选配置文件）</p><p><code>mqConfig.xml</code>的主要作用在于保证<code>rabbitmq</code>消息队列的可用性，保证<code>exchange</code>、<code>queue</code>和对应<code>bind</code>的有效性。</p><p>一般来说如果需要用到<code>rabbitmq</code>，推荐编写此配置，若用户能保证<code>rabbitmq</code>的可用性，可以不修改此配置文件。</p><h3 id="taskConfig-xml"><a href="#taskConfig-xml" class="headerlink" title="taskConfig.xml"></a>taskConfig.xml</h3><p><code>resources</code>-&gt;<code>config</code>-&gt;<code>taskConfig.xml</code>（可选配置文件）</p><p><code>taskConfig.xml</code>的主要作用在于创建一些定时任务。</p><h3 id="consumerConfig-xml"><a href="#consumerConfig-xml" class="headerlink" title="consumerConfig.xml"></a>consumerConfig.xml</h3><p><code>resources</code>-&gt;<code>config</code>-&gt;<code>consumerConfig.xml</code>（可选配置文件）</p><p><code>consumerConfig.xml</code>的主要作用在于创建<code>rabbitmq</code>的队列消费者，<span style="color:red">一般来说需要配置此文件</span>。</p>]]></content>
      
      
